class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Domain\\Tool\\BeforeToolCallContext"
type: readonly final class
summary: "This readonly final class encapsulates the immutable context required before a tool execution, bundling the assistant's message, the specific tool call, and its arguments. It serves as a structured data carrier to pass execution state through the agent's processing pipeline without exposing mutable state."
